{"word":"μετατίθημι","slug":"μετατίθημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μετατίϑημι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μετά\">μετά</a>, τίϑημι</el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘make a change in position’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of spatial movement <b>transfer, take away <a href='B:510 7:16'>Ac 7:16</a>; <a href='B:650 11:5'>Hb 11:5</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense, of transferring allegiance, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> pejorative connotation <b>distance oneself, desert <a href='B:550 1:6'>Gal 1:6</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘cause to be different’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> change <a href='B:650 7:12'>Hb 7:12</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> pervert <a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μετασχηματίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μετατρέπω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}